---
---
<section class="thank-you-steps-section">
  <h2>What Happens Next?</h2>
  <div class="steps-container">
    <div class="step-card">
      <div class="step-badge">STEP 1</div>
      <img src="/assets/images/thank-you/Contact Review.svg" alt="Contact Review" />
      <h3>Contact Review</h3>
      <p>A member of our local team will review your<br class="desktop-br"/>
contact information and your specific product<br class="desktop-br"/>
interest (Gates, Fences, or Pergolas).</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="step-divider"></div>

    <div class="step-card">
      <div class="step-badge">STEP 2</div>
      <img src="/assets/images/thank-you/The Callback.svg" alt="The Callback" />
      <h3>The Callback</h3>
      <p>A representative will call you shortly to discuss<br class="desktop-br"/>
your project ideas and schedule a convenient date<br class="desktop-br"/>
and time for your free on-site consultation.</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="step-divider"></div>

    <div class="step-card">
      <div class="step-badge">STEP 3</div>
      <img src="/assets/images/thank-you/On-Site Estimate.svg" alt="On-Site Estimate" />
      <h3>On-Site Estimate</h3>
      <p>We will meet at your property to take exact<br class="desktop-br"/>
measurements, discuss your design preferences,<br class="desktop-br"/>
and provide you with a detailed estimate.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .thank-you-steps-section {
    padding: 5rem 2rem;
    max-width: 1312px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .thank-you-steps-section h2 {
    color: #312C2C;
    text-align: center;
    font-family: 'Raleway', sans-serif;
    font-size: 45px;
    font-style: normal;
    font-weight: 800;
    line-height: 48px;
    letter-spacing: -0.9px;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
    margin-top: 0;
  }

  .steps-container {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 3rem;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .steps-container {
      flex-direction: row;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 1rem;
    }
  }

  .step-card {
    flex: 1;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    max-width: 400px;
  }

  .step-badge {
    display: flex;
    width: 261.5px;
    height: 36px;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    color: #FFF;
    text-align: center;
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 17px;
    font-style: normal;
    font-weight: 600;
    line-height: 24px;
    letter-spacing: 0.85px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    background-color: #2C65B0;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    position: relative;
    clip-path: polygon(0 0, calc(100% - 15px) 0, 100% 50%, calc(100% - 15px) 100%, 0 100%);
  }

  .step-card img {
    width: 85px;
    height: 85px;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .step-card h3 {
    color: #2C65B0;
    text-align: center;
    font-family: 'Raleway', sans-serif;
    font-size: 26px;
    font-style: normal;
    font-weight: 800;
    line-height: 24px;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    margin-top: 0;
  }

  .step-card p {
    color: #635C57;
    text-align: center;
    font-family: 'Raleway', sans-serif;
    font-size: 16px;
    font-style: normal;
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 22.75px;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .step-divider {
    display: none;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .step-divider {
      display: block;
      width: 1px;
      height: 321px;
      background: #E5E2DE;
      margin-top: 1rem;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 1100px) {
    .desktop-br {
      display: none;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .thank-you-steps-section h2 {
      font-size: 41px;
    }
  }
</style>
